Package: causalCalibration
Type: Package
Title: Causal Calibration for Heterogeneous Treatment Effects
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Lars", family = "van der Laan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lvdlaan@uw.edu")
  )
Description: Production-ready causal calibration, cross-calibration, and
    doubly robust calibration diagnostics for heterogeneous treatment effect
    predictors. The package provides framework-agnostic tooling for the methods
    introduced in the causal isotonic calibration paper and companion
    calibration-error diagnostics literature.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    reticulate,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
